.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: canadian, dutch, german, indian, mexican, pakistani, polish
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: epic, mystery, western, thriller, drama, crime, satire
 1. the mexican is on the left of the canadian##1
 2. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
 3. the person watching drama movies is the polish##1
 4. the german is on the left of the pakistani##1
 5. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 6. the indian is the person watching thriller movies##1
 7. the canadian is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 8. the person watching epic movies is between the person watching satire movies and the indian##2
 9. the canadian is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
10. the dutch is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Nationality   | polish | mexican | canadian | dutch   | indian | german | pakistani |
| Movie-Genre           | drama | crime     | mystery     | western | thriller   | epic   | satire    |

