.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, cain, prince, chaman, tiparillo, pall-mall, montecristo
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, chinese, malaysian, mexican, nigerian, pakistani, polish
 1. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the malaysian##1
 2. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the nigerian##1
 3. the pakistani is on the right of the mexican##1
 4. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the nigerian##1
 5. the australian is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
 6. the mexican is between the prince-smoker and the pakistani##2
 7. the aristoff-smoker is in the middle##1
 8. the mexican is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
 9. the cain-smoker is the chinese##1
10. the australian is the montecristo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Cigar      | prince    | tiparillo  | chaman  | aristoff  | montecristo      | pall-mall       | cain |
| Nationality   | nigerian | mexican | pakistani | polish | australian | malaysian | chinese  |

