.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: sudoku, collecting, board-games, filmmaking, baking, gardening, skydiving
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, motorbike, ship, skateboard, train, van
1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the person driving the bike is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person driving the bike is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
9. the person who's hobby is baking is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Hobby   | filmmaking      | baking | sudoku | board-games | skydiving      | collecting      | gardening |
| Transport     | helicopter | train | van       | bike | motorbike | skateboard | ship |

