.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
There 7 different types of food: watermelon, strawberry, pepper, lime, radish, pumpkin, kale
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, climbing, cycling, lacrosse, parkour, rowing, snowboarding
1. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating kale##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is the person eating radish##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
5. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person eating watermelon##2
7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
8. the person eating pumpkin is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Food     | radish | watermelon | lime | pumpkin | strawberry | pepper     | kale |
| Sport   | cycling   | lacrosse    | snowboarding    | parkour      | climbing  | badminton | rowing |

