.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, fanta, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, lemonade, milk
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: april, may, september, july, june, december, october
 1. the person who's birthday is in december is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking fanta is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in october##2
 5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is the person drinking coffee##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person drinking iced-tea##2
10. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Beverage   | coffee | cola    | hot-chocolate | fanta   | lemonade | milk    | iced-tea |
| Birthday      | july | april | october    | may | june    | september | december  |

