 7. the dressmaker is on the right of the police-officer##1
 8. the accountant is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 9. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing-polo##1
10. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person who's sport is climbing-polo##2
11. the photographer is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
