.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-11::.
7 different games are played: billiard, bridge, snooker, go, scrabble, mah-jongg, poker
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse, sailing, skateboarding, tennis, volleyball, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far right##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the person playing scrabble is in the middle##1
4. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
6. the person playing go is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person playing bridge##2
7. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person playing snooker and the person playing poker##2
8. the person playing poker is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
9. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |       2       |     3      |       4       |    5    |     6      |       7       |
| Game   | poker | mah-jongg       | snooker    | scrabble | go | bridge     | billiard       |
| Sport   | lacrosse    | skateboarding | volleyball | tennis        | sailing | ice-hockey | weightlifting |

