.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |      3      |   4    |    5    |   6   |    7     |
| Beverage      | 7up   | fanta | almond-milk | sprite | mirinda | tea   | iced-tea |
| Pet   | ferret | chinchilla | mouse     | cat | horse  | hedgehog | lizard     |

